# configx rules

Use `github.com/aisphereio/kernel/configx` for runtime configuration.

## Forbidden

```go
os.Getenv("X")
import "github.com/aisphereio/kernel/configx"
yaml.Unmarshal(data, &cfg)
```

## Required

```go
cfg := configx.New(configx.WithSource(file.NewSource("configs/app.yaml")))
_ = cfg.Load()
```

## Example lookup

| Scenario | Example |
|---|---|
| create config | `ExampleNew` |
| read typed value | `ExampleGet` |
| required startup value | `ExampleMustGet` |
| optional default | `ExampleGetOrDefault` |
| scan struct | `ExampleConfig_Scan` |
| watch key | `ExampleConfig_Watch` |
| layered sources | `ExampleBusiness_layeredFileAndEnv` |
| required config validation | `ExampleBusiness_validateRequiredConfig` |

Read `configx/README.md` and `docs/ai/configx.md` before writing config code.
